<text><body>
<cb:mulu n="5" level="1" type="品">5 供養品</cb:mulu><cb:mulu n="14" level="2" type="其他">14 無動金剛根本三昧耶印明</cb:mulu><cb:div type="pin">
<milestone n="3" unit="juan"/>
<pb n="0020b" ed="T" xml:id="T21.1201.0020b"/>
<lb n="0020b01" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0020b02" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="003" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="003" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead><note n="0020011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">乙丙兩本下卷缺之</note>底哩三昧耶不動尊聖者念誦祕
<lb n="0020b03" ed="T"/>密法卷<note n="0020012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此下甲本有高雄成身院經藏本八字</note><note n="0020012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">下【大】，下高雄成身院經藏本【甲】</note><app n="0020012"><lem wit="【大】">下</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">下高雄成身院經藏本</rdg></app></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0020b04" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0020b05" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator">大興善寺三藏沙門不空奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0020b06" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu n="15" level="2" type="其他">1 無動金剛寶山印</cb:mulu><head><note n="0020013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">次前甲本有不動金剛祕密要法品第六</note>無動金剛寶山印第一</head>
<lb n="0020b07" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT21p0020b0701" type="regular"><l>金剛堅固內相叉，<caesura/>是名寶山身密印，</l>
<lb n="0020b08" ed="T"/><l>種種供養并護身，<caesura/>加持本明頂上散。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0020b09" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu n="16" level="2" type="其他">2 無動金剛頭印</cb:mulu><head>無動金剛頭印第二</head>
<lb n="0020b10" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT21p0020b1001" type="regular"><l>禪度入掌把為拳，<caesura/>置安頂上名頭印，</l>
<lb n="0020b11" ed="T"/><l><note n="0020014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">思＝想【甲】</note><note n="0020014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">思【大】，想【甲】</note><app n="0020014"><lem wit="【大】">思</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">想</rdg></app>此全身聖者前，<caesura/>靜坐安心作觀照。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0020b12" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu n="17" level="2" type="其他">3 無動金剛髻印</cb:mulu><head>無動金剛<note n="0020015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">髻＝髮【甲】＊</note><note n="0020015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">髻【大】＊，髮【甲】＊</note><app n="0020015"><lem wit="【大】">髻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">髮</rdg></app>印第三</head>
<lb n="0020b13" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT21p0020b1301" type="regular"><l>戒方檀慧內相叉，<caesura/>忍願<note n="0020016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">堅＝竪【甲】</note><note n="0020016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">堅【大】，竪【甲】</note><app n="0020016"><lem wit="【大】">堅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">竪</rdg></app>合進力附，</l>
<lb n="0020b14" ed="T"/><l>禪智二度背相著，<caesura/>屈入戒方相叉內，</l>
<lb n="0020b15" ed="T"/><l>與二無名面相著，<caesura/>舉印置安左髻中，</l>
<lb n="0020b16" ed="T"/><l>是名無動金剛髻。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0020b17" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu n="18" level="2" type="其他">4 無動金剛眼印</cb:mulu><head>無動金剛眼印第四</head>
<lb n="0020b18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0020b1801">準前<note n="0020017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（金剛）＋髻【甲】</note><note n="0020017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">髻【大】，金剛髻【甲】</note><app n="0020017"><lem wit="【大】">髻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">金剛髻</rdg></app>印，翻手倒垂至額前，即名無動金剛
<lb n="0020b19" ed="T"/>眼。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0020b20" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu n="19" level="2" type="其他">5 無動金剛口印</cb:mulu><head>無動金剛口印第五</head>
<lb n="0020b21" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT21p0020b2101" type="regular"><l>檀慧二度內相叉，<caesura/>戒方雙押內叉上，</l>
<lb n="0020b22" ed="T"/><l>忍願竪合進力附，<caesura/>禪捻戒背智捻方，</l>
<lb n="0020b23" ed="T"/><l>是名聖者金剛口。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0020b24" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu n="20" level="2" type="其他">6 無動金剛心印</cb:mulu><head>無動金剛心印第六</head>
<lb n="0020b25" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT21p0020b2501" type="regular"><l>戒方檀慧內相叉，<caesura/>忍願竪合屈進力，</l>
<lb n="0020b26" ed="T"/><l>禪智並捻忍願文，<caesura/>是名無動金剛心。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0020b27" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu n="21" level="2" type="其他">7 無動金剛師子奮迅印</cb:mulu><head>無動金剛師子奮迅印第七</head>
<lb n="0020b28" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT21p0020b2801" type="regular"><l>準前無動金剛甲，<caesura/>唯改進力頭<note n="0020018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">相拄＝開立ィ【原】</note><note n="0020018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">相拄【大】，開立【校異-原】</note><app n="0020018"><lem wit="【大】">相拄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">開立</rdg></app>，</l>
<lb n="0020b29" ed="T"/><l>起立頻<note n="0020019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">伸虎＝申似ィ【原】</note><note n="0020019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">伸虎【大】，申似【校異-原】</note><app n="0020019"><lem wit="【大】">伸虎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">申似</rdg></app>舞勢，<caesura/>遶壇行道辟除魔，</l>
<pb n="0020c" ed="T" xml:id="T21.1201.0020c"/>
<lb n="0020c01" ed="T"/><l>師子頻伸大奮迅，<caesura/>是名五股金剛印。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0020c02" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu n="22" level="2" type="其他">8 無動金剛火印</cb:mulu><head>無動金剛火印第八</head>
<lb n="0020c03" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT21p0020c0301" type="regular"><l>禪捻三度背為拳，<caesura/>進度獨舒指定掌，</l>
<lb n="0020c04" ed="T"/><l>散開五度如猛焰，<caesura/>是名無動金剛火。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0020c05" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu n="23" level="2" type="其他">9 無動金剛法螺印</cb:mulu><head>無動金剛法螺印第九</head>
<lb n="0020c06" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT21p0020c0601" type="regular"><l>二羽各如無動劍，<caesura/>掌內鉤鎖狀<note n="0020020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">猶＝連ィ【原】，惠【甲】</note><note n="0020020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">猶【大】，連【校異-原】，惠【甲】</note><app n="0020020"><lem wit="【大】">猶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">連</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">惠</rdg></app>環，</l>
<lb n="0020c07" ed="T"/><l>忍願竪合頭相拄，<caesura/>進興忍背重相著，</l>
<lb n="0020c08" ed="T"/><l>力度願背亦如是，<caesura/>是名無動法螺印。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0020c09" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu n="24" level="2" type="其他">10 無動金剛索印</cb:mulu><head>無動金剛索印第十</head>
<lb n="0020c10" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT21p0020c1001" type="regular"><l>禪捻三度背為拳，<caesura/>進度直舒<note n="0020021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">觀＝止ィ【原】</note><note n="0020021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">觀【大】，止【校異-原】</note><app n="0020021"><lem wit="【大】">觀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">止</rdg></app>羽握，</l>
<lb n="0020c11" ed="T"/><l>力度屈捻智如環，<caesura/>是名無動金剛索。</l></lg>
<lb n="0020c12" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0020c1201"><note n="0020022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（印）＋明【甲】</note><note n="0020022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">明【大】，印明【甲】</note><app n="0020022"><lem wit="【大】">明</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">印明</rdg></app>曰：</p>
<lb n="0020c13" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT21p0020c1301">「曩麼三曼哆嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note><g ref="#CB00718"/>阿<note place="inline">引</note>波舍伴闍那
<lb n="0020c14" ed="T"/>吽泮吒<note place="inline">半音</note>」</p>
<lb n="0020c15" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT21p0020c1501"><l>無動金剛劍印明，<caesura/>能成就一切事業。</l></lg>
<lb n="0020c16" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0020c1601">明曰：</p>
<lb n="0020c17" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT21p0020c1701">「唵阿者羅迦拏<note n="0020023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【甲】</note><note n="0020023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">引【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0020023"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>勃馱制吒迦吽吽佉<note n="0020024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">醯＋（阿）【甲】</note><note n="0020024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">醯【大】，醯阿【甲】</note><app n="0020024"><lem wit="【大】">醯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">醯阿</rdg></app>佉
<lb n="0020c18" ed="T"/>醯伊能<note n="0020025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">魚＝迦ィ【原】</note><note n="0020025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">魚【大】，迦【校異-原】</note><app n="0020025"><lem wit="【大】">魚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">迦</rdg></app>哩<note place="inline">二合</note>醯摩<g ref="#CB00805"/>賀唎尾沙索鉢多<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0020c19" ed="T"/>合</note>惡紇哩<note place="inline">二合</note>訶吽<note place="inline">引</note>泮吒阿哩耶<note place="inline">二合</note>者羅阿
<lb n="0020c20" ed="T"/><note place="inline">引</note>蘖車緊至羅夜思伊<note place="inline">引</note>能迦哩羅耶<note n="0020026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二合〕－【甲】</note><note n="0020026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二合【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0020026"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>句
<lb n="0020c21" ed="T"/>嚕<note n="0020027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">耶＝那【甲】</note><note n="0020027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">耶【大】，那【甲】</note><app n="0020027"><lem wit="【大】">耶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">那</rdg></app>麼莎縛<note place="inline">二合</note>訶」</p>
<lb n="0020c22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0020c2201">持明行者每常食時，出一分殘食供養本尊
<lb n="0020c23" ed="T"/>像，歡喜擁護所求皆得，終不空過。復誦無動
<lb n="0020c24" ed="T"/>金剛根本明。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0020c25" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu n="25" level="2" type="其他">11 無動金剛解界明印</cb:mulu><head>無動金剛解界明印第十一</head>
<lb n="0020c26" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0020c2601">持明行者念誦了，即解前所結火界及牆界
<lb n="0020c27" ed="T"/>已，灌頂印竪二小指頭相拄是也。當誦燈焰
<lb n="0020c28" ed="T"/>如來解界明，以印左轉即成解界，前火院界
<lb n="0020c29" ed="T"/>是也。燈焰如來解界真言曰：</p>
<pb n="0021a" ed="T" xml:id="T21.1201.0021a"/>
<lb n="0021a01" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT21p0021a0101">「曩麼悉底哩也<note place="inline">二合</note>陀嚩拏哦哆喃唵紇哩<note place="inline">二合</note>」</p>
<lb n="0021a02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0021a0201">誦密語已，重以香花如法供養，懺悔三業。即
<lb n="0021a03" ed="T"/>結部母印護身，方可起去，轉誦大乘方廣理
<lb n="0021a04" ed="T"/>趣，諸善事<note n="0021001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">隨＋（意）【甲】</note><note n="0021001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">隨【大】，隨意【甲】</note><app n="0021001"><lem wit="【大】">隨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">隨意</rdg></app>修行。</p>
<lb n="0021a05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0021a0501">持明行<note n="0021002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">者＋（者）【甲】</note><note n="0021002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">者【大】，者者【甲】</note><app n="0021002"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">者者</rdg></app>每<note n="0021003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">欲＝飲【甲】</note><note n="0021003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">欲【大】，飲【甲】</note><app n="0021003"><lem wit="【大】">欲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">飲</rdg></app>食時，以事業金剛真言加
<lb n="0021a06" ed="T"/>持自身中種子，加鑁字復誦十力明八遍乃
<lb n="0021a07" ed="T"/>食之。明曰：</p>
<lb n="0021a08" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT21p0021a0801">「曩麼三曼哆鑁」</p>
<lb n="0021a09" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0021a0901">十力明曰：</p>
<lb n="0021a10" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT21p0021a1001">「曩謨薩嚩母馱<g ref="#CB00155"/>地薩怛嚩<note place="inline">二合</note>喃唵麼蘭捺
<lb n="0021a11" ed="T"/>泥帝<note place="inline">引</note>孺<g ref="#CB04209"/><g ref="#CB00069"/>寧莎縛<note place="inline">二合</note>訶」</p>
<lb n="0021a12" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0021a1201">如是先成就本尊<note n="0021004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（飯）＋訖【甲】</note><note n="0021004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">訖【大】，飯訖【甲】</note><app n="0021004"><lem wit="【大】">訖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">飯訖</rdg></app>，所餘觸食以成辦諸事
<lb n="0021a13" ed="T"/>心明供養所應食者，當用不空威怒增加聖
<lb n="0021a14" ed="T"/>者不動尊明誦一遍，受者歡喜，當隨行者而
<lb n="0021a15" ed="T"/>護念之。每日如是供養不得斷絕，常得本尊
<lb n="0021a16" ed="T"/>護念，諸魔不能為害。施食已，如常禮懺依
<lb n="0021a17" ed="T"/>法念誦。於中夜分欲消息時，即結<note n="0021005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">先＝光【甲】</note><note n="0021005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">先【大】，光【甲】</note><app n="0021005"><lem wit="【大】">先</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">光</rdg></app>莊嚴
<lb n="0021a18" ed="T"/>印。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0021a19" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu n="26" level="2" type="其他">12 無動金剛光莊嚴印明</cb:mulu><head>無動金剛光莊嚴印明第十二</head>
<lb n="0021a20" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT21p0021a2001" type="regular"><l>慧手翻掌彎心上，<caesura/>定掌還來心上合，</l>
<lb n="0021a21" ed="T"/><l>加持本明安頂上，<caesura/>便開二手順身摩，</l>
<lb n="0021a22" ed="T"/><l>能除障難得成就，<caesura/>以護身故名莊嚴。</l></lg>
<lb n="0021a23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0021a2301">光莊嚴明曰：</p>
<lb n="0021a24" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT21p0021a2401">「曩麼悉底哩也<note place="inline">四合</note>陀嚩<note place="inline">二合</note>拏伽哆喃薩嚩怛
<lb n="0021a25" ed="T"/>他蘖哆喃摩訶三昧耶<note n="0021006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔伽底〕－【甲】</note><note n="0021006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">伽底【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0021006"><lem wit="【大】">伽底</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>伽帝<note n="0021007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔三曼帝〕－【甲】</note><note n="0021007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">三曼帝【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0021007"><lem wit="【大】">三曼帝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>三
<lb n="0021a26" ed="T"/>摩蘖羅嚩<note place="inline">二合</note>摩他薩<note n="0021008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔羅〕－【甲】</note><note n="0021008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">羅【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0021008"><lem wit="【大】">羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>婆多羅<note place="inline">二合</note>路計達
<lb n="0021a27" ed="T"/>麼馱埵底多僧伽帝莎嚩<note place="inline">二合</note>訶」</p>
<lb n="0021a28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0021a2801">作前法已，應如過去燃燈佛禮拜法，金剛合
<lb n="0021a29" ed="T"/>掌，長舒二臂於頂上，面東<note n="0021009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">令＝合【甲】</note><note n="0021009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">令【大】，合【甲】</note><app n="0021009"><lem wit="【大】">令</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">合</rdg></app>面著地，長展二
<pb n="0021b" ed="T" xml:id="T21.1201.0021b"/>
<lb n="0021b01" ed="T"/>足以心著地。如是禮拜時，觀念一切諸佛菩
<lb n="0021b02" ed="T"/><note n="0021010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">薩＋（名禮本剎復作是念我今當捨全身為僕供養一切諸佛菩薩）【甲】</note><note n="0021010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">薩【大】，薩名禮本剎復作是念我今當捨全身為僕供養一切諸佛菩薩【甲】</note><app n="0021010"><lem wit="【大】">薩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">薩名禮本剎復作是念我今當捨全身為僕供養一切諸佛菩薩</rdg></app>，唯願攝受我等作最上成就，哀愍故。如
<lb n="0021b03" ed="T"/>是三迴已後隨意消息，心念明相作速成就
<lb n="0021b04" ed="T"/>相。</p></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb n="0021b05" ed="T"/><cb:div type="pin"><cb:mulu n="6" level="1" type="品">7 無動金剛事業求願品</cb:mulu><head>無動金剛事業求<note n="0021011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">願＋（品）【甲】</note><note n="0021011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">願【大】，願品【甲】</note><app n="0021011"><lem wit="【大】">願</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">願品</rdg></app>第七</head>
<lb n="0021b06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0021b0601">爾時釋迦牟尼佛告執金剛菩薩言：「我今為
<lb n="0021b07" ed="T"/>汝說無量神通力無動金剛法，能利益成就
<lb n="0021b08" ed="T"/>一切事業。若修行者菜食長齋或菓子等，誦
<lb n="0021b09" ed="T"/>滿一萬遍已，於月八日或十五日一日一夜
<lb n="0021b10" ed="T"/>大作供養，於像前取苦練木和蘇燒，一呪一
<lb n="0021b11" ed="T"/>燒滿一千八遍。作此法已，然後所作一切事
<lb n="0021b12" ed="T"/>法皆得成就。行者出語令縛即縛，及問事等，
<lb n="0021b13" ed="T"/>能摧折樹木墮落飛鳥，能令一切泉池枯渴，
<lb n="0021b14" ed="T"/>亦能令人鬪諍獲勝。得此已，亦能團風而為
<lb n="0021b15" ed="T"/>一團。</p>
<lb n="0021b16" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0021b1601">「又法於月蝕夜，取<note n="0021012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">未＝木【甲】</note><note n="0021012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">未【大】，木【甲】</note><app n="0021012"><lem wit="【大】">未</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">木</rdg></app>著地牛糞塗曼荼羅，
<lb n="0021b17" ed="T"/><note n="0021013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">種＝三ィ【原】</note><note n="0021013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">種【大】，三【校異-原】</note><app n="0021013"><lem wit="【大】">種</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">三</rdg></app>種香花散於壇上，置大般若經前。取純色
<lb n="0021b18" ed="T"/>犢子牸牛蘇一兩，置熟銅椀中，取佉陀羅木
<lb n="0021b19" ed="T"/>為齒木，并攪蘇明不限遍數，令種種成就。</p>
<lb n="0021b20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0021b2001">「又山峯頂上不喫食，誦滿十萬遍，即得見一
<lb n="0021b21" ed="T"/>切伏藏。</p>
<lb n="0021b22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0021b2201">「又<note n="0021014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">用＝由【甲】＊</note><note n="0021014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">用【大】＊，由【甲】＊</note><app n="0021014"><lem wit="【大】">用</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">由</rdg></app>乳作火法誦一千八遍，沃火燒，能除疫
<lb n="0021b23" ed="T"/>病。若共一切人論議，即得彼人口噤不論。</p>
<lb n="0021b24" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0021b2401">「又法取句瀘草和蘇乳蜜，加持沃火中燒，誦
<lb n="0021b25" ed="T"/>十萬遍，能除大疫病。</p>
<lb n="0021b26" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0021b2601">「又取蓮花和蘇酪蜜，誦明沃火中燒，誦<note n="0021015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔明〕－【甲】</note><note n="0021015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">明【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0021015"><lem wit="【大】">明</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>十
<lb n="0021b27" ed="T"/>萬遍，蓮華吉祥天與行者願。</p>
<lb n="0021b28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0021b2801">「又法於臨<note n="0021016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">近＝江【甲】</note><note n="0021016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">近【大】，江【甲】</note><app n="0021016"><lem wit="【大】">近</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">江</rdg></app>海河口，入水至胸，誦明三十萬
<lb n="0021b29" ed="T"/>遍，得尾沙耶。</p>
<pb n="0021c" ed="T" xml:id="T21.1201.0021c"/>
<lb n="0021c01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0021c0101">「又誦明以華擲火中燒，隨華色得衣。燒穀米，
<lb n="0021c02" ed="T"/>得穀米。</p>
<lb n="0021c03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0021c0301">「又取尾邏縛木，誦明燒十萬遍，即得囉闍。</p>
<lb n="0021c04" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0021c0401">「又取必哩養隅木，誦明燒，能令一切人愛念。
<lb n="0021c05" ed="T"/>明柏木燒，即得無量僕從。明大麥燒，得為大
<lb n="0021c06" ed="T"/>長者。</p>
<lb n="0021c07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0021c0701">「次說畫像法。畫無動尊，身著赤土色帬衣，左
<lb n="0021c08" ed="T"/>垂辮<app type="star" corresp="#0020015"><lem wit="【大】">髻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">髮</rdg></app>，眼斜視，手執劍索，坐寶蓮華，嚬眉
<lb n="0021c09" ed="T"/>嗔面，作怖三<note n="0021017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">世＝界【原】</note><note n="0021017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">世【大】，界【原】</note><app n="0021017"><lem wit="【大】">世</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】">界</rdg></app>狀。如是畫已，於流水河海岸
<lb n="0021c10" ed="T"/>上如法安像。行者自身亦著赤色衣，心無染
<lb n="0021c11" ed="T"/>著寂靜乞食為活。於像前誦五十萬遍畢已，
<lb n="0021c12" ed="T"/>即於夜中以薝蔔木火燒，一明一燒擲火中
<lb n="0021c13" ed="T"/>滿一萬遍，即見無動聖者現前，自身得為如
<lb n="0021c14" ed="T"/>來使者，得三摩地共菩薩同位。</p>
<lb n="0021c15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0021c1501">「又法取尸陀林中帛，畫無動金剛像，以自身
<lb n="0021c16" ed="T"/>血淡作色。安置像面向<note n="0021018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔西〕－【甲】</note><note n="0021018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">西【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0021018"><lem wit="【大】">西</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>著，行者面向東坐
<lb n="0021c17" ed="T"/>念誦，每<note n="0021019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">時＝日【甲】</note><note n="0021019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">時【大】，日【甲】</note><app n="0021019"><lem wit="【大】">時</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">日</rdg></app>三時澡浴著濕衣，對像面前誦明
<lb n="0021c18" ed="T"/>十萬遍，即施一切鬼神食。又於黑月八日夜，
<lb n="0021c19" ed="T"/>取摩奴沙坐其上，誦明一萬遍已，彼摩奴沙
<lb n="0021c20" ed="T"/>動身，行者必不得怕。彼口現出大開敷蓮華，
<lb n="0021c21" ed="T"/>即把取，能令行者身如十五六童子，<app type="star" corresp="#0020015"><lem wit="【大】">髻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">髮</rdg></app>如連
<lb n="0021c22" ed="T"/>環，遊歷<note n="0021020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（梵）＋天【甲】</note><note n="0021020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">天【大】，梵天【甲】</note><app n="0021020"><lem wit="【大】">天</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">梵天</rdg></app>地得大明王。</p>
<lb n="0021c23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0021c2301">「又於像前每日<note n="0021021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二＝三【甲】</note><note n="0021021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二【大】，三【甲】</note><app n="0021021"><lem wit="【大】">二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">三</rdg></app>時念誦，隨力供養，燒沈水
<lb n="0021c24" ed="T"/>香。如是滿足六月，自見得尾沙耶主。</p>
<lb n="0021c25" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0021c2501">「又法取旗幡，誦明一千遍，執於軍陣前，能破
<lb n="0021c26" ed="T"/>他<note n="0021022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">陣＝障【甲】</note><note n="0021022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">陣【大】，障【甲】</note><app n="0021022"><lem wit="【大】">陣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">障</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0021c27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0021c2701">「又法欲禁他軍令不得動者，於旗幡上畫無
<lb n="0021c28" ed="T"/>動尊，身作黃肉色，四面上下出牙，四臂，作怖
<lb n="0021c29" ed="T"/>畏瞋怒狀，遍身火焰，作吞他兵勢。持法人以
<pb n="0022a" ed="T" xml:id="T21.1201.0022a"/>
<lb n="0022a01" ed="T"/>旗示彼人，又想聖者以羂索縛<note n="0022001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">彼＋（彼）ィ【原】</note><note n="0022001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">彼【大】，彼彼【校異-原】</note><app n="0022001"><lem wit="【大】">彼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">彼彼</rdg></app>兵眾，彼即
<lb n="0022a02" ed="T"/>無能動也。</p>
<lb n="0022a03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0022a0301">「四面無動金剛明曰：</p>
<lb n="0022a04" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT21p0022a0401">「曩麼三曼哆嚩日羅<note place="inline">二合</note><g ref="#CB00718"/>始麼<note place="inline">二合</note>舍囊悉體
<lb n="0022a05" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合</note>迦播羅楞訖哩<note place="inline">二合</note>哆戶怛嚩賀姥儞<g ref="#CB00768"/>嚩
<lb n="0022a06" ed="T"/><note place="inline">引</note>路囉馱縛<note place="inline">二合</note>能瑟吒邏<note place="inline">二合</note>迦囉邏娜捨曩
<lb n="0022a07" ed="T"/>步惹誐跛哩吠瑟徵擔捨唎邏<note n="0022002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">底榮＝勞【甲】</note><note n="0022002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">底榮【大】，勞【甲】</note><app n="0022002"><lem wit="【大】">底榮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">勞</rdg></app>捺<note n="0022003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囉＋（二合）細註【甲】</note><note n="0022003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">囉【大】，囉<note place="inline">二合</note>【甲】</note><app n="0022003"><lem wit="【大】">囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">囉<note place="inline">二合</note></rdg></app>
<lb n="0022a08" ed="T"/><note n="0022004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔曩〕－【甲】</note><note n="0022004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">曩【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0022004"><lem wit="【大】">曩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>野曩迦賀護<note n="0022005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔姥〕－【甲】</note><note n="0022005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">姥【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0022005"><lem wit="【大】">姥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>訖哆<note place="inline">二合</note>吒賀三者咄姥
<lb n="0022a09" ed="T"/>佉尾訖哩<note place="inline">二合</note>怛嚕<note place="inline">引</note>跛莽賀避沙拏也怛儞也
<lb n="0022a10" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合</note>他唵尾訖哩哆尾迦吒尾<note n="0022006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">迦＋（羅）【甲】</note><note n="0022006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">迦【大】，迦羅【甲】</note><app n="0022006"><lem wit="【大】">迦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">迦羅</rdg></app>邏摩賀<note n="0022007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囉＝跛【甲】</note><note n="0022007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">囉【大】，跛【甲】</note><app n="0022007"><lem wit="【大】">囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">跛</rdg></app>
<lb n="0022a11" ed="T"/><g ref="#CB02740"/><note place="inline">二合</note>哆尾瑟他姥怛羅契駐<note place="inline">尼去反</note>齒瑟吒賀囉
<lb n="0022a12" ed="T"/>案怛囉莽羅馱羅者咄姥母佉入嚩<note place="inline">二合</note>邏<note n="0022008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">那＋（迦）ィ【原】，（佉）【甲】</note><note n="0022008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">那【大】，那迦【校異-原】，那佉【甲】</note><app n="0022008"><lem wit="【大】">那</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">那迦</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">那佉</rdg></app>
<lb n="0022a13" ed="T"/>比路馱嚩<note place="inline">二合</note>計奢吽嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>嚩日<g ref="#CB00942"/><note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0022a14" ed="T"/>蘖羅<note place="inline">二合</note>吽泮吒莎嚩<note place="inline">二合</note>訶」</p>
<lb n="0022a15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0022a1501">「若欲令他相鬪者，取鳥鴿鵄梟羽<note n="0022009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">明＋（明）【甲】</note><note n="0022009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">明【大】，明明【甲】</note><app n="0022009"><lem wit="【大】">明</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">明明</rdg></app>燒，即得
<lb n="0022a16" ed="T"/>鬪諍。</p>
<lb n="0022a17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0022a1701">「若欲令燒設都嚕卒者，取稻糠燒。當燒之時，
<lb n="0022a18" ed="T"/>想聖者以索縛彼捨都嚕，將向南方，困苦吐
<lb n="0022a19" ed="T"/>血。彼等族類皆不得存也。</p>
<lb n="0022a20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0022a2001">「又法欲令設都嚕卒，取<note n="0022010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">土＝生【甲】</note><note n="0022010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">土【大】，生【甲】</note><app n="0022010"><lem wit="【大】">土</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">生</rdg></app>鹽蠟，苦練葉相和
<lb n="0022a21" ed="T"/>擣為泥，捻作彼形狀，置地上斫斷，即卒。</p>
<lb n="0022a22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0022a2201">「若明稻穀燒，令彼捨都嚕<note n="0022011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">即＋（卒）【甲】</note><note n="0022011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">即【大】，即卒【甲】</note><app n="0022011"><lem wit="【大】">即</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">即卒</rdg></app>貧窮。</p>
<lb n="0022a23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0022a2301">「若欲令大人愛樂者，<note n="0022012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔以鹽…又〕十九字－【甲】</note><note n="0022012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（以鹽…又）十九字【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0022012" cb:word-count="19"><lem wit="【大】">以鹽作彼形狀，段段斫
<lb n="0022a24" ed="T"/>之。誦滿七日，彼即愛樂。又</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>取俱蘇摩花<note n="0022013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">明＋（燈）【甲】</note><note n="0022013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">明【大】，明燈【甲】</note><app n="0022013"><lem wit="【大】">明</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">明燈</rdg></app>
<lb n="0022a25" ed="T"/>燒十萬遍，得夜叉女來，於三事中所求皆得。</p>
<lb n="0022a26" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0022a2601">「又明曼荼羅花，稱彼人名，即令<note n="0022014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">橫＝狂ヵ【原】</note><note n="0022014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">橫【大】，狂【考偽-原】</note><app n="0022014"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">橫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">狂</rdg></app>亂。</p>
<lb n="0022a27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0022a2701">「明鹽燒，即得天女來，所使隨意。</p>
<lb n="0022a28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0022a2801">「明安息香燒者，得<note n="0022015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">闍羅＝羅闍【甲】</note><note n="0022015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">闍羅【大】，羅闍【甲】</note><app n="0022015"><lem wit="【大】">闍羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">羅闍</rdg></app>歡喜。</p>
<lb n="0022a29" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0022a2901">「又畫像法。先畫釋迦牟尼佛<note n="0022016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">像＋（傍）ィ【原】，像＝傍【甲】</note><note n="0022016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">像【大】，像傍【校異-原】，傍【甲】</note><app n="0022016"><lem wit="【大】">像</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">像傍</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">傍</rdg></app>，畫文殊師利
<pb n="0022b" ed="T" xml:id="T21.1201.0022b"/>
<lb n="0022b01" ed="T"/>童子像，畫執金剛菩薩作微<g ref="#CB00764"/>面，手執金剛
<lb n="0022b02" ed="T"/>杵。於執金剛下，畫無動聖者種種莊嚴。即
<lb n="0022b03" ed="T"/>於彼前誦明<note n="0022017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">五十＝十五ィ【原】</note><note n="0022017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">五十【大】，十五【校異-原】</note><app n="0022017"><lem wit="【大】">五十</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">十五</rdg></app>萬遍，然後作一切事皆得
<lb n="0022b04" ed="T"/>稱意。</p>
<lb n="0022b05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0022b0501">「若欲令降他兵，即結無動聖者眼印，作瞋怒
<lb n="0022b06" ed="T"/>聲稱吽字。以心想令魍魎捉彼，乃降。<note n="0022018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（又法）ィ＋取【原】</note><note n="0022018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">取【大】，又法取【校異-原】</note><app n="0022018"><lem wit="【大】">取</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">又法取</rdg></app>尸
<lb n="0022b07" ed="T"/>陀林灰加持七遍與彼人，即得愛樂。</p>
<lb n="0022b08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0022b0801">「又法取牛黃加持七遍，點自身額上，能令眾
<lb n="0022b09" ed="T"/>人見者愛樂，毘那夜迦不能損害，熾焰成就
<lb n="0022b10" ed="T"/>故。</p>
<lb n="0022b11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0022b1101">「又法於己身上布明梵字，彼羅剎眾退散百
<lb n="0022b12" ed="T"/>由旬外。又被毒蛇，經半年不差，明之即差。</p>
<lb n="0022b13" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0022b1301">「又於壁上畫劍契，又畫句律迦大蛇纏劍上，
<lb n="0022b14" ed="T"/>其劍周圍有火焰。即加持千遍，以示病者，病
<lb n="0022b15" ed="T"/>者即下語。加持一百八遍，病者常蒙聖者擁
<lb n="0022b16" ed="T"/>護。每日加持殘食，置淨處供養聖者，常得如
<lb n="0022b17" ed="T"/>願。</p>
<lb n="0022b18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0022b1801">「行者瞋怒結心印稱吽字，一切惡雲退散。</p>
<lb n="0022b19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0022b1901">「又取棘針和羅視迦油明燒，能止大雨，能令
<lb n="0022b20" ed="T"/>行者成結大界，亦成就千種事業。</p>
<lb n="0022b21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0022b2101">「又說無動尊金剛畫像法。身著<note n="0022019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">赤＝亦【甲】</note><note n="0022019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">赤【大】，亦【甲】</note><app n="0022019"><lem wit="【大】">赤</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">亦</rdg></app>土色衣，左
<lb n="0022b22" ed="T"/>垂辮<app type="star" corresp="#0020015"><lem wit="【大】">髻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">髮</rdg></app>，斜視，童子狀，手執金剛杵及寶棒，眼
<lb n="0022b23" ed="T"/>微赤，坐石上，瞋怒，遍身火焰。於像前結愛樂
<lb n="0022b24" ed="T"/>一切印契，皆得成就。依前法作所樂騰空隱
<lb n="0022b25" ed="T"/>形及所愛法，隨意成就。縱無畫像，獨處閑靜
<lb n="0022b26" ed="T"/>或在寺中或山窟中離雜閙處，所求者一切
<lb n="0022b27" ed="T"/>皆得成就。</p>
<lb n="0022b28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0022b2801">「加持患瘧病者，即自縛下語。</p>
<lb n="0022b29" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0022b2901">「加持鏡，亦得像現，問事皆說。</p>
<pb n="0022c" ed="T" xml:id="T21.1201.0022c"/>
<lb n="0022c01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0022c0101">「取童子或童女置道場中，召神入令下壇中，
<lb n="0022c02" ed="T"/>問一切事皆得。</p>
<lb n="0022c03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0022c0301">「次欲成就繫迦羅法，於月一日日中<note n="0022020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">時＋（像前）【甲】</note><note n="0022020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">時【大】，時像前【甲】</note><app n="0022020"><lem wit="【大】">時</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">時像前</rdg></app>，著種
<lb n="0022c04" ed="T"/>種香華供養，不歇誦明一百八遍，念壇中一
<lb n="0022c05" ed="T"/>切諸佛菩薩。每日念誦，滿一月日，如法供養
<lb n="0022c06" ed="T"/>已，<app type="star" corresp="#0021014"><lem wit="【大】">用</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">由</rdg></app>苦練木柴燒火，遏迦木上塗蘇，白芥
<lb n="0022c07" ed="T"/>子加持燒火，從黃昏燒火至夜半。乃至日出，
<lb n="0022c08" ed="T"/>繫迦攞即來，語行者言：『使我作何事？』行者攝
<lb n="0022c09" ed="T"/>受已後，常隨行者，所使必得隨順。乃至使往
<lb n="0022c10" ed="T"/>天上取天女，即將來。所須飲食齒木水等，皆
<lb n="0022c11" ed="T"/>得給侍。」</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0022c12" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="003" fun="close"><cb:jhead>底哩三昧耶無動尊聖者念誦祕密法卷下</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0022c13" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0022c14" ed="T"/><cb:div type="w"><p xml:id="pT21p0022c1401">復次如前建立曼荼羅，應取一千蓮華，一
<lb n="0022c15" ed="T"/>華一誦安中台以為奉獻。然後引弟子入，
<lb n="0022c16" ed="T"/>告三昧耶言<note place="inline">為諸欲清淨誓</note>羯磨曼荼羅品。</p>
<lb n="0022c17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0022c1701">復次成就像法，於清淨絹<g ref="#CB00626"/>上畫觀自在
<lb n="0022c18" ed="T"/>菩薩，堅蘇彌盧頂八佛圍遶，白月一日於
<lb n="0022c19" ed="T"/>此像前。</p>
<lb n="0022c20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0022c2001">延享三丙寅年秋七月再校了，同臘月
<lb n="0022c21" ed="T"/>上旬彫刻成</p>
<lb n="0022c22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0022c2201">　　　　　　豐山長谷輪下無等誌</p></cb:div>
</body></text></TEI>